### Slots

| Slot | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `default` | Button label or custom inline content rendered after the optional icon / loading spinner. |

### SplitButton Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `variant` | `'primary' \| 'secondary' \| 'ghost' \| 'danger' \| 'success' \| 'warning' \| 'info'` | `primary` | Visual variant shared by the primary and menu buttons. |
| `size` | `'sm' \| 'md' \| 'lg' \| 'large' \| 'small' \| 'mini'` | `md` | Button density; aliases normalize to `sm`, `md`, or `lg`. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | `false` | Disables both the primary action and menu trigger. |
| `loading` | `boolean` | `false` | Shows the primary spinner and disables both interactive zones. |
| `icon` | `string` | - | Icon class shown before the primary label while not loading. |
| `menuIcon` | `string` | `i-ri-more-2-line` | Icon class used by the menu trigger slot fallback. |
| `menuDisabled` | `boolean` | `false` | Disables only the menu trigger in addition to global disabled/loading state. |
| `menuWidth` | `number` | `200` | Popover width passed to `TxPopover`. |
| `menuPlacement` | `'top-start' \| 'top-end' \| 'bottom-start' \| 'bottom-end' \| 'right-start' \| 'right-end' \| 'left-start' \| 'left-end'` | `bottom-end` | Popover placement. |
| `menuOffset` | `number` | `8` | Popover offset in pixels. |

### SplitButton Events

| Event | Params | Description |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| `click` | `(event: MouseEvent)` | Emitted by the primary button when not disabled or loading. |
| `menuOpenChange` | `(open: boolean)` | Emitted whenever the internal popover open state changes. |

### SplitButton Slots

| Slot | Props | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| `default` | - | Primary action label. |
| `menu` | `{ close: () => void }` | Menu content rendered inside `TxPopover`; call `close()` from menu actions after selection. |
| `menu-icon` | - | Replaces the default more icon in the menu trigger. |

